#Clean/reshape data
import re
class clsCleanData():
    def __init__(self,Colmn):
        self.strCol=Colmn
    def FuncRentFloor(self):
        lstRentFloor=[]
        for i in self.strCol:
            strTempFloor=i.split(' ')
            if(strTempFloor[0]=='Upper'):
                lstRentFloor.append('Upper Basement')
            elif(strTempFloor[0]=='Lower'):
                lstRentFloor.append('Lower Basement')
            else:
                lstRentFloor.append(strTempFloor[0])
        return lstRentFloor
    def FuncTotalFloor(self):
        lstTotalFloor=[]
        for j in self.strCol:
            strTempTFloor=j.split(' ')
            k=len(strTempTFloor)
            if(strTempTFloor[k-1]=='Upper'):
                lstTotalFloor.append('Upper Basement')
            elif(strTempTFloor[k-1]=='Lower'):
                lstTotalFloor.append('Lower Basement')
            else:
                lstTotalFloor.append(strTempTFloor[k-1])
        #print(len(lstTotalFloor))
        return lstTotalFloor
    def FuncContact(self):
        lstContactFinal=[]
        for strContact in self.strCol:
            #print(strContact)
            lstContactFinal.append(re.sub("Contact","",strContact))
        return lstContactFinal
